Ø       On-Line  
and Distance Education edited by Betty Collis


Ø       TeleEducation  
NB, Bibliography


Ø       The  
Virtual Classroom by Starr Roxanne Hiltz


Ø       Web  
Based Instruction by Badrul Huda Kahn (Editor)


Ø       Virtual  
Communities, by Howard Rheingold


 


